item.title: Ron DeSantis takes on Donald Trump
item.description:
After launching his presidential campaign, Florida Governor Ron DeSantis is sharing some of his ideas for the presidency.  CNN Political Director David Chalian breaks down DeSantis’ views on the executive branch and potential pardons for January 6th rioters. Plus, the governor’s attacks against former President Donald Trump have turned pointed since his announcement.
